{"type":"message","id":"8c1d3b86","parentId":"19389e12","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:00:11.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering reminder relaying**\n\nI think I need to relay a reminder related to a scheduled task. It's probably helpful to make sure I scan the skills that apply, especially since the rules are always active for the feishu channel. I’ve read earlier notes, so I wonder if this might not be necessary? Still, I should recall to \"scan available skills\" before replying, so a short answer will probably suffice.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 老大，12:00 的【高频轻巡检】提醒到了。\n\n这轮只看短线风险，不做长分析，重点盯：\n- OKX 真实仓位，尤其 DOGE-USDT-SWAP\n- 浮盈亏有没有明显扩大/收窄\n- 关键位有没有被有效突破或失守\n- 风险暴露是不是上升了\n- 建议有没有从“继续观察”变成“该处理了”\n\n规则还是一样：如果只是小波动、结论没变、还在原区间震荡，就不该打扰你；只有出现明显变化，才会用最多 3 句给你结论，并明确是否符合用户规则。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":35905,"output":275,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36180,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775275200097,"responseId":"resp_090b5f132dfc40950169d08cc468108191a4c051fb63257d63"}}
